Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassroomsDailyTime
    Implementation of the interface IClassroomsDailyTime through the usage of a Map that as a key shows the values of Classrooms.values() and to everyone it is associated a IDailyTime.
    DailyTime
    Implementation of the interface IDailyTime through the usage of a List of elements that represent all the hours of the day.
    Model
    Implementation of the interface IModel through a Map with semester as key and as associated value IWeeklyTime and a Set of ISubject for the list of available courses.
    Subject
    Implementation of the interface ISubject.
    WeeklyTime
    Implementation of the interface IWeeklyTime through the use of a Map that has the values of Days.values() as key and it has associated to everyone a IClassroomsDailyTime.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Classrooms
    Enumerator class used to represent available classroom inside the faculty of informatics science and technology in Cesena.
    Days
    Enumerator class in order to represent days in which lessons are hold at the university.
    SubjectType
    Enumerator class that represents all the different types concerning courses.
